{"tid":628292,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"傳美國擬升級貿易戰 或禁中國投資美科技業","createTime":"2018-04-13T16:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T05:55:45.000Z","uid":13663,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c2f87a01a363957b9702337c413e0f911caa9390","tid":628292,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T16:41:27.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普對中國貿易問題的態度近日似乎有所軟化，不過有傳美國將就中美貿易戰採取進一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n華爾街日報引述消息指，美國總統特朗普計劃透過向中國加徵新關稅及威脅永久禁止中國投資美國科技業，向中國施壓。<br />\n另外，美國擬就1000億美元總值的中國商品施加25%關稅，報道指美國最早將於下周公佈詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180413/large/1523632134_72af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180413%2Flarge%2F1523632134_72af.jpg&h=32adde6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b0a5602d38f0433832ffdf495d90d4af8efe515","tid":628292,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T16:41:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180413/58070607\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180413%2F58070607&d=mszPkrQQoR4xrLvcE5owStr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=756d00c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180413%2F58070607&h=f34a8aee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180413/58070607</a>"},{"pid":"f199ab7d122a56edad157d13fa4991a35a1b87d4","tid":628292,"uid":177736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T17:24:50.000Z","msg":"有心食住上  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"892385b615c399e42323fd7cd8f0e7381d2f25a9","tid":628292,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T18:18:17.000Z","msg":"做實事"},{"pid":"794fa2f886ac7810f8aa236ae90ce778ca95fac7","tid":62